eu.first.RIM

Class Reporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.first.RIM.Reporter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PrettyHTML5Reporter, PrettyReporter

    public class Reporter
extends java.lang.Object
    Reporter class. Has three functions: (1) storing results of all product/client data (input and output data as stored in a Data object), (2) accumulating statistic at a counterpart, product, client and bank level and (3) making external reports.
    Since:
    2012-10-22
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Marko Bohanec (marko.bohanec@ijs.si)
